titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MEDIUM CHAIN ACYL-COA DEHYDROGENASE DEFICIENCY) - Description

body.p: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MEDIUM CHAIN ACYL-COA DEHYDROGENASE DEFICIENCY) is the same as attribute NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS .
NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (MEDIUM CHAIN ACYL-COA DEHYDROGENASE DEFICIENCY) is the result of screening for Medium Chain Acyl-CoA Dehydrogenase Deficiency (MCADD).
